Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ここに たしかに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:16.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君といた証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:21.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ずっと スピラーレ
